nodes.text: Dotswa Ween chaired the RCLU in 22 BBY. On the eleventh day of the fourth month of that year, the chairbeing made an appearance on a talk show called In the Political Pit at 1935.

Dotswa Ween was mentioned in an issue of the HoloNet News feed (2002), Volume 531, Issue 51, that was published in-universe. The section that referenced the individual, titled "What to Scan," was written by Pablo Hidalgo and Paul Ens.
